---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
import '../../styles/guided-tool.css';
---

<Base title="Future Prototypes - May">

  <section class="tool-hero">
    <span class="tool-label">tool 07</span>
    <h1>Future Prototypes</h1>
    <p class="tool-intro">
      Instead of deciding everything in your head, design 3 small tests.
      To experience a life before quitting everything - because the best way to choose is by living.
    </p>
    <p class="tool-origin">Based on Design Your Life - Bill Burnett & Dave Evans</p>
  </section>

  <div class="divider"></div>

  <section class="guided-experience" id="experience">

    <!-- Resume prompt -->
    <div class="resume-prompt">
      <p></p>
      <div class="resume-actions">
        <button class="btn-primary btn-resume">continue</button>
        <button class="btn-secondary btn-restart">start over</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Unified fractal visualization -->
    <div class="fractal-viz" id="fractal-viz"></div>

    <!-- Transition screen -->
    <div class="transition-screen">
      <div class="transition-dots"><span>.</span><span>.</span><span>.</span></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Completion breath -->
    <div class="completion-breath">
      <div class="breath-text"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 0: Intro -->
    <div class="step active" data-step="0">
      <div class="step-content">
        <p class="step-context">
          Design Your Life proposes that we treat life as a design project:
          instead of trying to get it right the first time, you create prototypes - small, cheap,
          and reversible versions - to test if something makes sense before committing.
        </p>
        <p class="step-context">
          Here you'll move from "I should do X" to "how do I test X without quitting everything."
        </p>
        <button class="btn-primary step-next">begin <span class="arrow">→</span></button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 1 -->
    <div class="step" data-step="1">
      <div class="step-header">
        <span class="step-number">1 de 6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="ai-insight">
          <span class="ai-insight-marker">✦ reflection</span>
          <p class="ai-insight-text"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-encouragement"></div>
        <h2>What do you want to explore?</h2>
        <p class="step-guide">
          Describe the change, idea, or path you're considering.
          It could be a career, a lifestyle, a project, a different relationship with work.
          What's in your head wanting to come out?
        </p>
        <textarea id="q1" placeholder="What I want to explore is..." rows="5"></textarea>
        <div class="step-nav">
          <button class="btn-secondary step-prev"><span class="arrow">←</span> back</button>
          <button class="btn-primary step-next">next <span class="arrow">→</span></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 2 -->
    <div class="step" data-step="2">
      <div class="step-header">
        <span class="step-number">2 de 6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="ai-insight">
          <span class="ai-insight-marker">✦ reflection</span>
          <p class="ai-insight-text"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-encouragement"></div>
        <h2>Why haven't you tested it yet?</h2>
        <p class="step-guide">
          What's stopping you? Fear? Lack of time? Not knowing where to start?
          What would need to be true for you to feel safe enough to try?
        </p>
        <textarea id="q2" placeholder="I haven't tested it yet because..." rows="5"></textarea>
        <div class="step-nav">
          <button class="btn-secondary step-prev"><span class="arrow">←</span> back</button>
          <button class="btn-primary step-next">next <span class="arrow">→</span></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 3 -->
    <div class="step" data-step="3">
      <div class="step-header">
        <span class="step-number">3 de 6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="ai-insight">
          <span class="ai-insight-marker">✦ reflection</span>
          <p class="ai-insight-text"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-encouragement"></div>
        <h2>Prototype 1 - The conversation</h2>
        <p class="step-guide">
          The simplest prototype is a conversation. Who already lives something similar to what you want?
          Who could give you a real perspective - not an idealized one? Describe who you'd seek out
          and what you'd ask.
        </p>
        <textarea id="q3" placeholder="I'd talk to... and ask..." rows="5"></textarea>
        <div class="step-nav">
          <button class="btn-secondary step-prev"><span class="arrow">←</span> back</button>
          <button class="btn-primary step-next">next <span class="arrow">→</span></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 4 -->
    <div class="step" data-step="4">
      <div class="step-header">
        <span class="step-number">4 de 6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="ai-insight">
          <span class="ai-insight-marker">✦ reflection</span>
          <p class="ai-insight-text"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-encouragement"></div>
        <h2>Prototype 2 - The experience</h2>
        <p class="step-guide">
          How could you live a piece of that life for a short period?
          A week working differently, a day in a new place, a side project,
          volunteering, an intensive course. What experience would give you a real taste?
        </p>
        <textarea id="q4" placeholder="I could try..." rows="5"></textarea>
        <div class="step-nav">
          <button class="btn-secondary step-prev"><span class="arrow">←</span> back</button>
          <button class="btn-primary step-next">next <span class="arrow">→</span></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 5 -->
    <div class="step" data-step="5">
      <div class="step-header">
        <span class="step-number">5 de 6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="ai-insight">
          <span class="ai-insight-marker">✦ reflection</span>
          <p class="ai-insight-text"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-encouragement"></div>
        <h2>Prototype 3 - The pilot project</h2>
        <p class="step-guide">
          If you could create something small - a project, a service, an offer, an experiment —
          that would truly test this idea, what would it be? Something you can start
          in the next 30 days, without asking permission.
        </p>
        <textarea id="q5" placeholder="My pilot project would be..." rows="5"></textarea>
        <div class="step-nav">
          <button class="btn-secondary step-prev"><span class="arrow">←</span> back</button>
          <button class="btn-primary step-next">next <span class="arrow">→</span></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Step 6 -->
    <div class="step" data-step="6">
      <div class="step-header">
        <span class="step-number">6 de 6</span>
      </div>
      <div class="step-content">
        <div class="ai-insight">
          <span class="ai-insight-marker">✦ reflection</span>
          <p class="ai-insight-text"></p>
        </div>
        <div class="step-encouragement"></div>
        <h2>Which prototype do you do first?</h2>
        <p class="step-guide">
          Of the three prototypes - conversation, experience, pilot project - which is most feasible now?
          Which gives you the most information for the lowest cost? Choose one and set a start date.
        </p>
        <textarea id="q6" placeholder="I'll start with the prototype... because... and I'll begin..." rows="5"></textarea>
        <div class="step-nav">
          <button class="btn-secondary step-prev"><span class="arrow">←</span> back</button>
          <button class="btn-primary" id="finish-btn">see my prototypes <span class="arrow">→</span></button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Result -->
    <div class="step" data-step="result">
      <div class="step-content result-content">
        <h2>Your prototypes</h2>
        <p class="result-intro">Three ways to test your idea - without quitting everything, without deciding in your head.</p>

        <div class="result-block"><h3>What I want to explore</h3><p id="r1"></p></div>
        <div class="result-block"><h3>What's stopping me</h3><p id="r2"></p></div>
        <div class="result-block"><h3>Prototype 1 - The conversation</h3><p id="r3"></p></div>
        <div class="result-block"><h3>Prototype 2 - The experience</h3><p id="r4"></p></div>
        <div class="result-block"><h3>Prototype 3 - The pilot project</h3><p id="r5"></p></div>
        <div class="result-block closing-block"><h3>My first prototype</h3><p id="r6"></p></div>

        <div class="reflection-prompt">
          <span class="reflection-label">a question to take with you</span>
          <p class="reflection-text">What's the smallest action that turns "I want to do" into "I'm doing"?</p>
        </div>

        <div class="reflection-counter"></div>

        <div class="result-actions">
          <button class="btn-secondary" id="copy-btn">copy text</button>
          <button class="btn-secondary" id="download-btn">save as text</button>
          <button class="btn-secondary" id="save-journal-btn">save to journal</button>
          <button class="btn-secondary" id="restart-btn">redo ↺</button>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<script>
  import { GuidedTool } from '../../scripts/guided-tool';
  import { initToolVisuals } from '../../scripts/tool-visuals';

  if (!(window as any).__guidedToolInit) {
    (window as any).__guidedToolInit = true;

  const config = {
    slug: 'prototipos-de-futuro',
    totalSteps: 6,
    fields: [
      { input: 'q1', output: 'r1' },
      { input: 'q2', output: 'r2' },
      { input: 'q3', output: 'r3' },
      { input: 'q4', output: 'r4' },
      { input: 'q5', output: 'r5' },
      { input: 'q6', output: 'r6' },
    ],
    encouragements: [
      '',
      'Putting desire into words is already an act of courage.',
      'Understanding what blocks you is the first step to unblocking.',
      'The right conversation can change the entire perspective.',
      'Actually trying is worth more than imagining in your head.',
      'A pilot project is the safest way to test a life.',
      'Choosing the first step is more important than having the perfect plan.',
    ],
    closingReflection: 'What\'s the smallest action that turns "I want to do" into "I\'m doing"?',
    resultTitle: 'Future Prototypes',
    visualConfig: {
      type: 'prototype-bench',
      sections: [
        { id: 'tema', label: 'theme', stepRange: [1], wordClass: 'genuine' },
        { id: 'obstaculo', label: 'obstacle', stepRange: [2], wordClass: 'fear' },
        { id: 'prototipo-conversa', label: 'prototype 1', stepRange: [3], wordClass: 'strategy' },
        { id: 'prototipo-experiencia', label: 'prototype 2', stepRange: [4], wordClass: 'strategy' },
        { id: 'prototipo-piloto', label: 'prototype 3', stepRange: [5], wordClass: 'strategy' },
        { id: 'escolha', label: 'choice', stepRange: [6], wordClass: 'genuine' },
      ],
    },
  };

  const tool = new GuidedTool(config);
  tool.init();
  GuidedTool.wireExport(config);
  initToolVisuals(config.slug);

  }
</script>
